Package flight_system

Class Summary
Airplane Class used to represent an airplane based on the information provided by the XML files in the flight database system.
Airport Class used to represent an airport based on the information provided by the XML files in the flight database system.
Date Class used to a date based on the information provided by the XML files in the flight database system.
Flight Class used to represent a flight.
FlightFilter Class used to represent a flight filter based on flights.
FlightLeg Class used to represent a flight leg based on the information provided by the XML files in the flight database system.
FlightSystem The Main Flight System application.
Location Class used to represent location in latitude and longitude.
Prototype  
Tester  
Time Class used to represent time in hours and minutes.
UserInfo Class used to store a user's trip and search criteria information.
